François Morel (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7ois_Morel_(actor) 0 François Morel (born 10 June 1959) is a French actor and filmmaker. He is best known for appearing in sketch television series Les Deschiens (1993-2002). François_Morel ( born_10_June_1959 ) is a_French_actor_and_filmmaker . He is_best_known for appearing in sketch_television_series_Les_Deschiens_(_1993-2002_) .
